Package org.cloudsimplus.builders.tables.vmstatistics

package org.cloudsimplus.builders.tables.vmstatistics
A package with classes for calculating/printing statistics for trace-based simulations.
Since:
CloudSim Plus 7.3.2
Author:
Pavlos Maniotis
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    TimeStatsTableBuilder
    A class for calculating the Min, Avg, Max, Variance, and Stddev statistics on a list of values.
    VmTypeRecordsTableBuilder
    A class for creating histograms about the VM types, i.e., VmTypeRecord.
